{"tid":759753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣深高鐵停駛　乘客被困挨餓中暑　疑獲派過期食物","createTime":"2018-07-29T02:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T04:00:30.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a07ac25774f57fd8a00ad3dbf42715cb4ed0f7f3","tid":759753,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T02:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180729/s00004/e3c074fdda83fb966b75f5e92d86d0df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180729%2Fs00004%2Fe3c074fdda83fb966b75f5e92d86d0df.jpg&h=a6604fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180729/s00004/e1ed7df8e736bf73c444cff24e47d1cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180729%2Fs00004%2Fe1ed7df8e736bf73c444cff24e47d1cf.jpg&h=9a6c55b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180729/s00004/e1ed9f22d2f9defb217b95b6f07b117c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180729%2Fs00004%2Fe1ed9f22d2f9defb217b95b6f07b117c.jpg&h=f5e6a121&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣深高鐵昨日下午一度全線停運，持續時間大概4小時，有多班列車取消，直至晚間8時半左右才復運。廣鐵集團表示，事件由常平至東莞站間的設備故障所致。<br />\n<br />\n據報停運期間，沿線不少乘坐「和諧號」列車旅客，被困於無電無冷氣車廂內捱餓。有網民透露，部分車廂內多人中暑暈倒，車務人員不但禁止乘客離開車廂，同時也沒有分發任何應急物資，甚至連一樽水也沒有，因此有人不滿起鬨，要求車務人員「管飯（供應飯食）」。<br />\n<br />\n當局事後致歉，並解釋因廣深線是短途列車，故車上準備餐飲不多。他們又呼籲購買已停運列車車票旅客，可在30日內到就近車站辦理免費退票。<br />\n<br />\n另外，報道指，部分被困乘客抵達常平後，獲車務人員分發小吃及安排上自費接駁巴士返回深圳，不過食物卻是過期的。根據乘客在微博上載的包裝袋圖片顯示，餅乾疑已過期逾兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180729/s00004/1532823807380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180729%2Fs00004%2F1532823807380&d=EiDfJdQdG%2FZi7HAVwIfDtCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ceb6fe53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180729%2Fs00004%2F1532823807380&h=26cfff3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180729/s00004/1532823807380</a>"},{"pid":"7098298e99a868fb009a0ba489bdb7d93e7480cb","tid":759753,"uid":82640,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:07:31.000Z","msg":"以前去上海睇世博<br />\n坐火車都試過咁<br />\n<br />\n有飯盒派但全部過期<br />\n支那文化黎<br />\n自己做錯補救都唔願用錢<br />\n<br />\n所以呢啲國家之後就冇去過<br />\n堂堂贏國奧運世博都搞過<br />\n仲一潭死水擺明無心改善"},{"pid":"c6a4751b8f7fdda180cb76539379641f07f2908e","tid":759753,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:24:59.000Z","msg":"中國狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6054fba5610bba00ed4e8190a54467c84ad4d72b","tid":759753,"uid":61257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3001068385ac22af79012b7eb7e8d30fafce4e2","tid":759753,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:40:12.000Z","msg":"先進國家係咁㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"704fdf44ee601ced4599dce0a6afabc093d4efed","tid":759753,"uid":97494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:44:23.000Z","msg":"有野食派已經算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0976ddee98634754a580f1310ab662b6a8f8770b","tid":759753,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"過期先好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e3ccc9c15b526e6a456c56297db018f81841e3","tid":759753,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc60497036e98a2f5d822f43dea6433aa4d5294","tid":759753,"uid":3773,"like":0,"disli